Use python 3.7 or 3.7.6
use pycharm
after creating the project add a new folder name it "Resources" and move the haarcascade frontal face xlm to it
install opencv-python for importing cv2(watch a video on how to add libraries or how to install packages in pycharm projects)
i used opencv-python version 4.2.0.32 you can also use the same or use other version
change videocapture from 0 to 1 if you are using a extra webcam on pc or if you are using a pc
